<div class="bodyText intro">
    <div>Welcome to the developer site for the RChain platform. This is a hub for content to help you learn about and get started with RChain. This is also a hub for developers who want to participate in the project or plan to build on the RChain platform. If you don't find what you need, please see the <a href="faq">FAQ</a> or post your question in the <a href="https://forum.rchain.coop/" target="_blank">forum</a>.</div>
